# Crust local environment overrides.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values you don't want committed.
# `.env*` is gitignored, so secrets stay on your machine. Vite inlines these
# at build/dev time, so setting them during `pnpm build` will bake the value
# into the production bundle — keep them out of CI unless you mean it.
#
# All VITE_GIF_* variables override the matching field in public/config.json.

# VITE_GIF_ENABLED=true
# VITE_GIF_PROVIDER=giphy
# VITE_GIF_API_KEY=your-dev-api-key-here
# VITE_GIF_TRENDING_ON_OPEN=true
# VITE_GIF_MAX_RATING=g
